11#ifndef RTC_BASE_NUMERICS_HISTOGRAM_PERCENTILE_COUNTER_H_
12#define RTC_BASE_NUMERICS_HISTOGRAM_PERCENTILE_COUNTER_H_
13
14#include <stddef.h>
15#include <stdint.h>
16
17#include <map>
18#include <vector>
19
20#include "absl/types/optional.h"
21
22namespace rtc {
23// Calculates percentiles on the stream of data. Use |Add| methods to add new
24// values. Use |GetPercentile| to get percentile of the currently added values.
25class HistogramPercentileCounter {
26 public:
27 // Values below |long_tail_boundary| are stored as the histogram in an array.
28 // Values above - in a map.
29 explicit HistogramPercentileCounter(uint32_t long_tail_boundary);
30 ~HistogramPercentileCounter();
31 void Add(uint32_t value);
32 void Add(uint32_t value, size_t count);
33 void Add(const HistogramPercentileCounter& other);
34 // Argument should be from 0 to 1.
35 absl::optional<uint32_t> GetPercentile(float fraction);
36
37 private:
38 std::vector<size_t> histogram_low_;
39 std::map<uint32_t, size_t> histogram_high_;
40 const uint32_t long_tail_boundary_;
41 size_t total_elements_;
42 size_t total_elements_low_;
43};
44} // namespace rtc
45#endif // RTC_BASE_NUMERICS_HISTOGRAM_PERCENTILE_COUNTER_H_
